The paper discusses the vulnerabilities and security concerns in robotics, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also presents an online playground for challenging robot security, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) aspects. Additionally, the use of scenarios and challenges for hacking robots involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques.
